{
  "stem": "5430.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was right after they, they came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this is just like a flash, back flash.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then all I remember, they picked out this old man and started cutting the beard with the bayonet, like, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and they were just laughing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was one of the-- pardon?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not too friendly either, unfortunately, because right after when they came in, and they started doing some propaganda by throwing out loaves of bread from a truck to, to the population.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and I ran one day, and I was in the bunch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of my own neighbors started yelling, Juden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't give him bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was right after the invasion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You would think it was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very bad, very angry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, these are the people who we grew up with, and supposedly you made friendly relationship.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my father, having been the pillar of the neighborhood, you know, it's a-- he supposedly had friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But unfortunately, some of them came to my father and mother and they said, ha, now we'll get you, Jew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hitler will take care of you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's when we knew that things were bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And but even, even during the invasion when they started bombing the city, we had occasion where the-- when the building started to burn from the incendiary bombs.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father [INAUDIBLE] said, kindala, we got to save our things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The building-- well, no, the building where we lived, which is 110, only a couple blocks away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The restaurant was a low building, a one story building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But where we lived was a four story house.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
